data_case_c_nesting
#
# Case C: apo (70%) vs bound (30%); the bound state nests two ligand poses (0.20 + 0.10 = 0.30).
# Tyr120 carries the protein conformation, LIG301 is the ligand. The nesting forbids a ligand
# co-occurring with apo, with NO exclusion row. base = everything single-conformer (not listed).
#
